# Plan Completion Gate (Protocol)

## Scope

- Applies to: `.cursor/plans/*.plan.md`
- Excludes: `.cursor/plans/archive/*`

When ALL todos are `completed`, the agent MUST:

1. Update `.cursor/plans/ACTIVE.plan.md` (current → last completed)
2. Update plan `last_updated` (ISO 8601 with seconds)
3. Link evidence report if created

See project ACTIVE.plan template for format.
